# MISC::IS_THIS_A_MINIGAME_SCRIPT

## Summary
Checks that this is a mingame script

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
It is possible for more than one minigame script to be running at the same time.
